<h2 class="sectionedit6"><a name="access_to_the_cloud_infrastructure" id="access_to_the_cloud_infrastructure">Access to the Cloud Infrastructure</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>

The project maintains a <a href="referenceservices" class="wikilink1" title="referenceservices">cloud infrastructure for tests</a>.  We will allow access to a limited number of people external to the project.  If you are interested in testing the StratusLab distribution, please send an email to the support mailing list.

</p>

</div>

<h2 class="sectionedit7"><a name="packages" id="packages">Packages</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>

The software packages for this release are:
</p>
<ul>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> OpenNebula (one-2.0-StratusLab-0.1.0-1, RPM)</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> Command Line Interface for Users (stratuslab-cli-user-1.1-1, TAR, RPM)</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> Command Line Interface for Sys. Admins (stratuslab-cli-sysadmin-1.1-1, TAR, RPM)</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> StratusLab Web Monitor (stratuslab-web-monitor-1.1-1, RPM)</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> Benchmarks (stratuslab-benchmarks-1.0-1, RPM)</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> OpenNebula Quattor Config. Module (ncm-oned-1.2.1-1, RPM)</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> Libvirtd Quattor Config. Module (ncm-libvirtd-1.0.1-1, RPM)</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> Quattor Cloud Config. (quattor-cloud-config-0.1.1, TAR)</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> <strong>New in v0.2</strong>: Cloud Proxy (stratuslab-cloud-proxy, RPM) </div>
</li>
</ul>

<p>

The release also includes virtual machine base images:
</p>
<ul>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> ttylinux 9.5</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> Ubuntu 10.04</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> CentOS 5.5</div>
</li>
</ul>

<p>
which are available from the <a href="http://appliances.stratuslab.eu/images/" class="urlextern" title="http://appliances.stratuslab.eu/images/"  rel="nofollow">appliance repository</a>.

</p>

